About This Company
We are a medium sized public accounting firm founded in Dubai in the year 1995. Our high quality professional audit, accountancy, business development and advisory services form the foundation of our practice.
Our clients represent virtually every field of business, industry, the professions, the arts and entertainment world.
We are affiliated to INPACT International Ltd., UK, a rapidly expanding network of independent accountancy and professional services firms (currently ranking 15th in the world) with members and affiliates throughout the world. The range and diversity of skills and technical expertise available within Ethics Plus and through our affiliation provides us with the resources to respond to every client situation throughout the United Arab Emirates and internationally.
At Ethics Plus, we focus our wealth of knowledge on the goals of each client and our philosophy is to be our clients most valued and trusted advisor.
